headline: If I Could Only Buy and Hold a Single Stock, This Would Be It.
summary: The company owns a massive portfolio of high-quality real estate.  Realty Income has a 5.6% dividend yield and a great track record of total returns.  The conglomerate is designed to perform well no matter what the economy is doing, and its diverse collection of stocks and subsidiaries essentially makes it a broad investment portfolio in a single stock.
